snippet.title: NEO Impossible Bosses Launch Trailer -  RTS-MOBA Boss Rush Game
snippet.description:
NEO Impossible Bosses is a RTS-MOBA Boss Rush game in which you (and optionally friends) control a number of heroes to take on the Impossible Bosses! 
Buy/Wishlist now on Steam at http://store.steampowered.com/app/676580/NEO_Impossible_Bosses/
Purchase on Itch.io at https://x0to1.itch.io/neoimpossiblebosses/

Website: http://neoimpossiblebosses.coder-ddeng.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/x0to1
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com
